title: Ep 2674 - The Act
shortDesc: After Sodhi is taken to Dr. Hathi to get inspected, Sodhi tells him that he is completely fine and he is acting so that he can get out of the mess he is into. He tells everyone about the back story regarding the act. What will Sodhi do now?

title: Ep 2675 - Leaving for the Party
shortDesc: Sodhi finally returns to his house as the Gokuldham society members believe that he has a stomach ache. Sodhi and Popatlal decide to leave Gokuldham but they have to do so without being seen by anyone.

title: Ep 2676 - Cross Questioning
shortDesc: Sodhi's friends to meet him are on the way to Gokhuldhaam. Sodhi tries to reach them but his phone is dead and his friends turn up at Bhide's house and start asking questions. Jethalal is caught in the cross fire of questions! Stay tuned!

title: Ep 2677 - The Party Begins
shortDesc: As the party has started for Sodhi, Madhavi remembers that in all this haste, she forgot to ask Popatlal for dinner and wants to call him for dinner. Jethalal smartly takes care of the situation but they have a bigger trouble coming towards them.

title: Ep 2678 - The Truth is Out
shortDesc: Jethalal tries to stop Roshan from entering her house but in vain as Roshan, in order to check on Sodhi, decides to enter her house. Roshan doesn't find Sodhi and calls him up.

title: Ep 2679 - Men Gang In Trouble
shortDesc: Champaklal gets angry and he asks for the whole truth. Taarak tells Champaklal about where Sodhi and Popatlal are. Champaklal takes up the hockey stick and runs after them to hit them. A scared Jethalal has locked himself up in his house.

title: Ep 2681 - Sodhis Confession
shortDesc: After the whole of Gokuldhaam has arrived on the scene, Roshan gives Sodhi a chance to explain himself, where he narrates the situation as it happened. Roshan isn't ready to belive Sodhi and threatens him with her going to her parents house.

title: Ep 2682 - The Result
shortDesc: As everything has ended on a good note between Sodhi and Roshan, Gokuldham society members look forward to a new day. Champaklal is elated after learning that Sonu's essay has been shortlisted for the national essay competition.

title: Ep 2683 - The Workshop
shortDesc: Sonu has topped the essay competition and gets a chance to go on a workshop to Delhi. Sonu is dejected after finding out that the workshop is for one month. Tapu Sena comes to know that Bhide will not allow Sonu to attend the workshop.

title: Ep 2684 - Sonu Goes To Delhi
shortDesc: Tapu Sena along with the ladies club, try to convince Bhide, that if Sonu misses the workshop she will be missing a huge opportunity in her life, the worries are always the same for every parent.

title: Ep 2685 - Search for Popatlals Bride
shortDesc: Popatlal begins his search for a bride and calls up Asit Kumarr Modi. Popatlal then calls up various marriage bureaus and requests them to find a prospective bride for him.

title: Ep 2686 - The Misunderstanding
shortDesc: Popatlal rushes to the marriage bureau with Bhide to meet the two women who have shown interest in his profile. But, things don't turn out as expected and Popatlal is dejected after finding out that there is a misunderstanding.

title: Ep 2687 - The Disappointment
shortDesc: The ladies of Gokuldham society decide to cheer up a dejected Popatlal but following the fiasco at the marriage bureau, Popatlal is heartbroken and is in no mood to mingle.

title: Ep 2668 - The Dilemma
shortDesc: Jethalal arrives at Babita's house but Iyer isn't pleased. Meanwhile, Sodhi is troubled by a situation as he isn't able to attend a wedding due to a hectic work schedule. Sodhi is worried that he might disappoint his wife.

title: Ep 2688 - Popatlals Misery
shortDesc: The Gokuldham society members try to cheer up Popatlal but Popatlal is dejected following the fiasco at the marriage bureau. Popatlal shouts at Bhide and Taarak Mehta and leaves for his house, wishing not to mingle with the society members.
